            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>An<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>i</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> Iusta <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LXXX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ita</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied> <expan><abbr>Ter</abbr><ex>entius</ex></expan> Lupus <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">mat</supplied>ri et <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Tere<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>tius</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">Ur</supplied>sulus <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan>? <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan></supplied> XIIII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">opti</supplied>mae <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Im Hauptbild oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Rosette in Kranz mit Schleifen, oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes Weinranken. Z. 7 Statt vet(eranus) möglicherweise auch mil(es), falls das Lebensalter der Mutter annähernd akkurat ist eher Veteran. Z. 8 möglicherweise [mat(ri) opti]m(a)e oder ähnliche Epitheta, oder [matri be(ne)] me(renti). Z. 1: NI-Ligatur; Z. 2: XXX ligiert und teilweise in Winkel des L eingeschrieben Z. 3: TE- Ligatur; Z. 4: ET-Ligatur; Z. 8: ME-Ligatur. (B): Z. 5: Krüger: ma]tri.</p>
            </div>
